      <title>利比亚央行僵局加剧，行长不愿让步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/libyan-central-bank-standoff-deepens-as-governor-won-t-back-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的利比亚央行行长坚持抵制罢免他的企图，这加深了敌对派系之间为争夺这个四分五裂的欧佩克国家巨额石油收入控制权而持续一周多的僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/libyan-central-bank-standoff-deepens-as-governor-won-t-back-down</guid>
